                                                                                                <b>Eda Button</b>
                    <p class="utterance">I said already. And he knew that my child was hidden in Saloniki.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Yes.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Eda Button</b>
                    <p class="utterance">And he said to me, &#34;What do you have to be here for? [unintelligible] from one house to another. And it is better you should drive to Spain. There you will breathe fresh air and be free and one month later you will return.&#34;</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Yes.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Eda Button</b>
                    <p class="utterance">And in the end I also asked the consul. The consul told me, &#34;It is the best for you, you have to drive to Spain.&#34;</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Yes.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Eda Button</b>
                    <p class="utterance">&#34;In five days you will be in Barcelona and you will be free.&#34; Then I came home, with the, the priest</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
