                    <p class="utterance">Yes.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Eda Button</b>
                    <p class="utterance">I said, &#34;This is now [unintelligible], are we allowed to travel? I am afraid and I want to go back to Athens. I do not want to travel. I do not want to go away.&#34;</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Yes.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Eda Button</b>
                    <p class="utterance">The wife of the Spanish consul then said to me, &#34;You are right but the Germans said it wrong, we were told you have to with second class . . . &#34;</p>
